Maintainer: Amber Runyon <amber_runyon@nps.gov>
Description: Using the functions in this package will enable users to  develop divergent scenarios of future climate (climate futures) from climate data and summarize 25 resource-relevant metrics of climate change. This package generates the climate materials used to support planning efforts by the National Park Service Climate Change Response Program. 
